File Menu:
New default board - CTRL + N
New custom-sized board - CTRL + C
Load board - CTRL + L
Save board - CTRL + S
Save board as - ALT + S
Exit - ALT + E

Competitive Play Mode:
Set objective - CTRL + O
Remove objective - CTRL + R
Set bounds - SHIFT + B
Remove bounds - SHIFT + R
Swap player colours - SHIFT + S
Make AI move - SHIFT + M
Set AI type - SHIFT + A

Problem Creation Mode:
Use black stones only - CTRL + B
Use white stones only - CTRL + W
Use mixed stones - CTRL + M
Delete stones - CTRL + D

Debug:
Do a Debug - ATL + D

Help:
Show Help - ATL + H

Buttons:
Competitive mode - ALT + P
Creation mode - ALT + C
Undo - ALT + U
Reset - ALT + R
Pass - ALT + A
Bounds - ALT + B